description:
The KATalyst Magazine - Volume 9 - September 2016.pdf

The KATalyst is the official magazine of KAT

The KATalyst Magazine is a bi-monthly publication. It was established early in 2015 by a collection of KAT super moderators, super users, and members.

Known as KAT's unofficial magazine, it has just been made the OFFICIAL magazine of KAT.

9 issues have been created so far, all of which feature member-produced content that called attention to KAT uploaders, poets, storytellers, and entertainment in general. 

KATalyst operates by the approval and authority of KAT Administration and works directly under the direction of MG. who is the Editor-In-Chief of the KATalyst Magazine. 

dollybird holds the title of Head Designer and Star.Sapphire is our Head Writer
